    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously sorted E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 high-revving V8. This isn't your average commuter; it\u2019s a precision instrument. I\u2019ve focused heavily on preventative maintenance\u2014rod bearings and throttle actuators are already addressed, ensuring the 8,400 RPM redline remains a safe playground. The chassis is taut thanks to upgraded bushings and a Bilstein B16 coilover setup that eliminates factory float without sacrificing compliance. The 6-speed manual gearbox is notch-free with a short-throw kit installed. While the exterior shows minor road patina consistent with an authentic driver\u2019s car, the mechanical heart is absolutely dialed-in. Ready for the canyons or the circuit.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
